                    <span>"Twist, belly-button, block." A major league relief pitcher taught me how to hit a baseball. An excellent book during an excellent time in Baseball.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Brosnan's book- Benign Ball Four Before Ball Four</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
